{"tid":1084872,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大家覺唔覺得天生嗰樣生得淋善好容易比人欺負","createTime":"2019-03-30T17:19:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-01T13:43:24.000Z","uid":179117,"like":59,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"e60d37ddef412835c074d433e82893dc80f3ef0a","tid":1084872,"uid":179117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T17:19:43.000Z","msg":"有人話見到我嗰樣就係天生比人蝦既樣<br />\n得罪我係完全無成本無後果<br />\n唔通嗰樣生得懦弱就註定俾人蝦咩？<br />\n之前係中女上司可以蝦我 今日連小學生都可以蝦我（人地態度差 我係唔敢駁嘴或者串翻佢轉頭<br />\n朋友都話 如果適當地西面可以避免不必要麻煩<br />\n份人太隨和太懦弱就會出事<br />\n雖然話由細到大 屋企人都教：人善人欺天不欺<br />\n但係我唔想再俾人欺喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n遲下畢業出社會做嘢點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有無師兄師姐可以教下我點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da47211118db51b58f30a2cd2bf47c5f08ab8ef9","tid":1084872,"uid":181581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T17:21:06.000Z","msg":"整容"},{"pid":"488d90b087de20550a832abee24849637b1b0312","tid":1084872,"uid":179117,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"da47211118db51b58f30a2cd2bf47c5f08ab8ef9","tid":1084872,"uid":181581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T17:21:06.000Z","msg":"整容"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T17:24:53.000Z","msg":"可惜從內而外的懦弱氣質無法改變"},{"pid":"35023032e95b045ec793163b6d2ea393da8124bd","tid":1084872,"uid":179117,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T17:27:44.000Z","msg":"有時候起度唸<br />\n嗰啲蝦人既人 係咪曾經都俾人蝦過（或者受氣<br />\n所以要蝦其他人先平衡到呢⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n但係將心比己 我係唔會成為自己曾經最痛恨既人（以後走去蝦人"},{"pid":"30b8ec77362a01b3b9b754360ef953b47b6d69dd","tid":1084872,"uid":181581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"488d90b087de20550a832abee24849637b1b0312","tid":1084872,"uid":179117,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"da472111